name: PHP-Spider
tagline: A configurable and extensible PHP web spider
body:
### Welcome to PHP-Spider.
Soon, you can find the complete documentation for the PHP-Spider here.
For now, you'll have to make do with the code in the /examples directory.

### Authors and Contributors
Matthijs van den Bos (@matthijsvandenbos)

### Support or Contact
Having trouble with the PHP-Spider? Find me on twitter (@matthijsvandenb).
